{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, an attention mechanism is introduced between graph convolution layers to jointly process node embeddings from each layer.",
    "Finally, drug-target interaction scores are predicted based on the embeddings of drugs and targets.",
    "This model uses fewer network types and demonstrates higher predictive performance.",
    "Nguyen et al.",
    "53 faced with insufficiently rich coronavirus datasets, enhanced data atomically and proposed a graph neural network method."
  ]
}